        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="arrow-box" id="arrow_3">
        <span>WHICH WILL</span>
        <i class="fa fa-chevron-down fa-3x"></i>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pow-scrolling-bg pow-bg-2 section">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="large-12 columns pow-home-content">
          <img ng-src="{{gif3Src}}" src="<%= asset_path('blank_gif.png') %>" data-tempsrc="<%= asset_path('landing/hauzz.gif') %>" class="gif3" id="gif_3_src" />
          <h4>Reverse climate change by turning millions of American homes clean, carbon-neutral, and energy independent.</h4>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="arrow-box" id="arrow_4">
        <span>SO WE</span>
        <i class="fa fa-chevron-down fa-3x"></i>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pow-scrolling-bg pow-bg-3 section">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="large-12 columns pow-home-content">
          <img ng-src="{{gif4Src}}" src="<%= asset_path('blank_gif.png') %>" data-tempsrc="<%= asset_path('landing/flame-grey.gif') %>" class="gif4" id="gif_4_src" />
          <h4>Create a sustainable, renewable and clean energy solution for all future generations.</h4>
        </div>
      </div>
     <div class="arrow-box" id="arrow_5">
       <i class="fa fa-chevron-down fa-3x"></i>
     </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pow-scrolling-bg  pow-bg-4 section inverted">
      <div class="pow-home-intro">
        <div class="row">
          <h1>The solar revolution is here.</h1>
        </div>
      </div>
     <div class="arrow-box inverted" id="arrow_6">
       <span>IT WILL BE DISRUPTIVE</span>
       <i class="fa fa-chevron-down fa-3x"></i>
     </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pow-scrolling-bg pow-bg-2 section landing-slide-8">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="large-12 columns pow-home-content">
          <h5>Select how you want to participate in the revolution.</h5>
          <div class="pow-buttons-wrapper">
            <a class="button pow-button-transparent" ng-href="/create-energy">ENERGY</a>
            <a class="button pow-button-solid" ng-href="/create-wealth">WEALTH</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <ng-include src="'shared/footer.html'"></ng-include>
    </div>
  </main>

